1. *Divlje* životinje su slobodne i nezavisne. (Wild animals are free and independent.)
2. Planina Tara ima prekrasnu *divlju* prirodu. (Mount Tara has beautiful wild nature.)
3. Vozili smo se kroz *divlju* vožnju na adrenalinskom parku. (We went through a wild ride at the adventure park.)
4. Čuo sam *divljeg* psa kako laje u šumi. (I heard a wild dog barking in the forest.)
5. *Divlja* svinja je opasna životinja. (A wild boar is a dangerous animal.)
6. Neki ljudi vole sakupljati *divlje* gljive u šumi. (Some people like to collect wild mushrooms in the forest.)
7. Kada je prestala kiša, oblaci su se razmaknuli i sunce se pojavilo iza *divljeg* brda. (When the rain stopped, the clouds cleared and the sun appeared behind a wild hill.)
8. Naše selo ima puno *divljih* životinja u okolnim šumama. (Our village has a lot of wild animals in the surrounding forests.)
9. U potoku koji protiče kroz planinu ima puno *divljih* riba. (The stream that flows through the mountain has a lot of wild fish.)
10. Ukoliko se ne ponašate pristojno, upasti ćete u *divlju* gomilu ljudi koja čeka pred trgovinom. (If you don't behave nicely, you'll get into a wild crowd of people waiting in front of the store.)